Description_lang: Deios blasts Nozdormu with corrupted bronze magic for $416264D, sending arcane artillery throughout the environment every $416264T1 sec, additionally inflicting $416290s1 Arcane damage to all players.The smaller bolts inflict $416265s1 Arcane damage to targets within $416265A1 yards, and the larger bolts inflict $416266s1 Arcane damage to targets within $416266A1 yards.
